        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_silence": "Silence",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_silence_Description": "Prevents enemy units in a target area from casting spells.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_silence_Lore": "Peering into the veil of her opponent's demise, Krobelus sees a silent future.",
