        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_witchcraft": "Witchcraft",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_witchcraft_Description": "Increases the potency of Death Prophet's spells, while providing a passive movement speed boost.  Reduces mana costs and cooldowns of Crypt Swarm and Silence, and adds additional spirits to Exorcism.",
