        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_exorcism": "Exorcism",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_exorcism_Description": "Unleashes evil spirits to drain the life of nearby enemy units and structures. At the end of the spell's duration, Death Prophet is healed in proportion to the damage dealt.  Lasts 30 seconds.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_exorcism_Lore": "Over time, the banshee remnants of her previous lives return to haunt the present.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_prophet_exorcism_radius": "RADIUS:",
