        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_templar_assassin_meld": "Meld",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_templar_assassin_meld_Lore": "Lanaya is as elusive as her covenant with the Hidden Temple.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_templar_assassin_meld_Description": "Templar Assassin conceals herself, gaining invisibility while remaining still.  On the next attacked enemy unit, Lanaya will reduce its armor and deal bonus damage to it.",
