        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_forged_spirit_melting_strike_Description": "Melts away the armor of heroes hit by the spirit's attack if the spirit has enough mana. Each successive hit increases the amount of armor melted.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_forged_spirit_melting_strike_armor_removed": "ARMOR REMOVED PER HIT:",
