        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_chaos_strike": "Chaos Strike",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_chaos_strike_Description": "Chaos Knight's mojo gives him a chance to deal bonus damage.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_chaos_strike_Lore": "Chaos Knight's unwieldy power bludgeons those who stand before him, crushing the thickest of armors.",
