        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_multicast": "Multicast",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_multicast_Description": "Enables the Ogre Magi to rapidly cast his spells, giving them greater potency. Gives a chance to cast a spell multiple times in one cast. Increases Fireblast's mana cost and decreases its cooldown, adds an area of effect to Ignite and reduces Bloodlust's cooldown and gives it a chance to cast on random allies around Ogre Magi.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.",
