        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_disruptor_static_storm_Description": "Creates a damaging static storm that also silences all enemy units in the area for the duration.  The damage starts off weak, but increases in power over the duration.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_disruptor_static_storm_Lore": "A summer squall in Druud is a hardship that only an Oglodi can survive.",
