        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_Description": "Ezalor turns his body luminescent temporarily, gaining various abilities.  Illuminate is now channeled by a separate spirit, and gains the Blinding Light and Recall abilities.",
